15 BE IT ENACTED BY THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF OKLAHOMA:
16 SECTION 1. AMENDATORY 70 O.S. 2021, Section 13-116, is
17 amended to read as follows:
18 Section 13-116. A. School district personnel shall be
19 prohibited from using corporal punishment on students any student
20 identified with the most significant cognitive disabilities
21 according to criteria established by the State Department of
22 Education unless addressed in an annual individualized education
23 program (IEP) developed a disability in accordance with the
24 Individuals with Disabilities Education Act (IDEA).
